sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM_Inf as vLLM Inference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLM_Emb as vLLM Embedding<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant VecDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant Search as Search API<br/>(Brave/Tavily)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (API key)
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: LLM response
    OGX->>PG: Log inference + store conversation<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>OGX: Ack
    OGX-->>Client: JSON response (chat completion)

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 2: Embedding + Vector Store
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>vLLM_Emb: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (API key)
    vLLM_Emb-->>OGX: Embedding vectors
    OGX->>VecDB: Store/query vectors<br/>TCP/HTTP/gRPC (TLS configurable)<br/>Auth: Token/Password/API key
    VecDB-->>OGX: Vector results
    OGX->>PG: Persist metadata<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>OGX: Ack
    OGX-->>Client: JSON response (embeddings)

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 3: Agentic Response with Tool Use
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/responses<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Initial inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: Response with tool_calls
    OGX->>Search: Execute tool: web search<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: API key
    Search-->>OGX: Search results
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Follow-up with tool results<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: Final response
    OGX->>PG: Log agent state + conversation<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>OGX: Ack
    OGX-->>Client: JSON response (agentic)
